    <published>2024-03-04T01:55:55.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-03-04T02:20:19.337Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>夙川惠璃，是一名病人。<br>诱因及疗法皆无法获知……<br>明白的只有它的致死性，以及名字——「樱纹病」</p><p>「一旦染上「樱纹病」，就只能伴随着恐惧死去」</p><p>可能得救的途径只有一个，令人绝望般的、心脏移植。<br>固然，现实中能找到适配的心脏就已经与奇迹同义。<br>为此才有着妹妹璃亚——经过基因调整的婴儿的诞生。<br>她生命的意义仅仅是为了给姐姐提供后备的心脏。</p><p>病魔缠身的姐姐，为她而活的妹妹。<br>除了姐妹的家族外，还有一人也知道这个残酷的秘密。<br>他是惠璃的友人・静峰龙次</p><p>你并不是替代品……</p><p>残余的时光，伴随着扭曲的觉悟、<br>各人心中交相错开的感情，所引向的前方是——</p><hr><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%2C%E3%80%90ADV-%E5%86%92%E9%99%A9%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E3%80%91/%E3%80%90PC%2B%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E3%80%91%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%B6/%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E3%81%AE%E3%82%B9%E3%83%9A%E3%82%A2.zip"   title="PC"><i class="red larger"></i><span>PC</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%2C%E3%80%90ADV-%E5%86%92%E9%99%A9%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E3%80%91/%E3%80%90PC%2B%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E3%80%91%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%B6/%E3%80%90KRKR%E3%80%91%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%B6.zip"   title="KR"><i class="red larger"></i><span>KR</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%2C%E3%80%90ADV-%E5%86%92%E9%99%A9%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E3%80%91/%E3%80%90PC%2B%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E3%80%91%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%B6/%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%B6.apk"   title="安卓直装"><i class="red larger"></i><span>安卓直装</span></a>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
