    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>猫娘乐园全家桶、巧克力与香子兰全家桶，NEKOPARA全家桶。</p><p>时间回到嘉祥担任店长的猫娘蛋糕店『La Soleil』开张的半年前，<br>还是小猫的巧克力跟香草刚来到水无月家，还没跟其他猫娘们打成一片的时候。<br>开始用「主人」称呼嘉祥，并且在水无月家度过第一个圣诞节的两人，和嘉祥立下了一个约定。<br>NEKOPARA OVA的众筹达标感谢礼，将为各位送上一段全新前传！<br>关于本游戏<br>NEKOPARA Extra是NEKOPARA视觉小说系列的众筹计划NEKOPARA OVA的延伸目标之一。惹人怜爱的两只猫娘，巧克力和香草又回来啦！这次的故事发生在NEKOPARA Vol.1之前，讲的是她们刚到水无月家中时发生的事。</p><hr><p>PC:</p><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%2C%E3%80%90ADV-%E5%86%92%E9%99%A9%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E3%80%91/%E3%80%90PC%2B%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E3%80%91%E5%B7%A7%E5%85%8B%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%8E%E9%A6%99%E5%AD%90%E5%85%B0/PC/Nekopara%20Vol.0.zip"   title="NEKOPARA0"><i class="red larger"></i><span>NEKOPARA0</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%2C%E3%80%90ADV-%E5%86%92%E9%99%A9%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E3%80%91/%E3%80%90PC%2B%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E3%80%91%E5%B7%A7%E5%85%8B%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%8E%E9%A6%99%E5%AD%90%E5%85%B0/PC/NEKOPARA%20Vol.%201.zip"   title="NEKOPARA1"><i class="red larger"></i><span>NEKOPARA1</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%2C%E3%80%90ADV-%E5%86%92%E9%99%A9%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E3%80%91/%E3%80%90PC%2B%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E3%80%91%E5%B7%A7%E5%85%8B%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%8E%E9%A6%99%E5%AD%90%E5%85%B0/PC/NEKOPARA%20Vol.%202.zip"   title="NEKOPARA2"><i class="red larger"></i><span>NEKOPARA2</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%2C%E3%80%90ADV-%E5%86%92%E9%